Subject: [PATCH 1/8] u_math: add ushort_to_float/float_to_ushort

v2:
- return 0 for NaN too

Cc: Roland Scheidegger <sroland@vmware.com>
Signed-off-by: Qiang Yu <yuq825@gmail.com>
---
